            <h1>International cooperation on rural and regional policy</h1>
            <div class="temaMobIngressImg" style="display: none;"></div>
            <p class="textIngress">Information regarding various Nordic, European and other international arenas for cooperation on regional policy.</p>
            
            <div class="descriptionTextFull"><p>Participation in international cooperation related to regional policy promotes cooperation and exchange of experience between the different regions and countries in Europe. The aim of such cooperation is to help further develop Norwegian regional policy and the role played by the county authorities in regional development, and to stimulate business development. Cooperation on international regional policy is also aimed at safeguarding Norwegian interests in connection with aspects such as the revision of European regional policy, government subsidy legislation and the expansion of the EU. <br /></p></div>
